HEADWORD: Ivan Ivanovitch
<hw>I*van" I*van"o*vitch</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>An
ideal personification of the typical Russian or of the Russian people;
-- used as ⟦ldquo⟧John Bull⟦rdquo⟧ is used for the typical
Englishman.</def>⟦br⟧
